summary:

As a dedicated recruiter, I am passionate about connecting top talent with roles that align with their career goals and aspirations. Recognized for my ability to build strong relationships with clients and candidates alike, as well as my proactive approach to talent acquisition, I have successfully placed candidates in roles across a range of industries and functional areas. 

My expertise spans the entire recruitment cycle, from sourcing and screening to interviewing and onboarding, and I stay up-to-date on industry trends and best practices to ensure that I am delivering the highest level of service to both clients and candidates.
